			<h3> O teor de clorofilas e carotenoides em azeites pode ser determinado usando um smartphone </h3>
			<div class="clorofilas">
				<embed src="https://scontent.fvcp10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75610863_2736614466383775_7895938121156526080_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&ccb=2&_nc_sid=cdbe9c&_nc_eui2=AeHdm0_dCyy_zdioMemSkXBCTmCJFpueqDVOYIkWm56oNXokr9RUd2PVSZX0bECcBd_mkZzllzRDzLGhlTBu9UhT&_nc_ohc=GHerfQusotEAX_4Z_Fc&_nc_ht=scontent.fvcp10-1.fna&oh=63de3a7990d10514c220bef82325526a&oe=5FDC2178" width = "755" height = "400">
